data.description: Embrace Your Urban Oasis in a great school zone with NO HOA! Stay high and dry safely away from any flooding. Situated on nearly a full acre, this exceptional property seamlessly marries the convenience of living in town with rare space and privacy. A whole-home generator and a complete top-to-bottom renovation ensures peace of mind, particularly in our hurricane-prone area. And let's not forget the detached workshop and garage, offering boundless possibilities. Dive into your resilient and versatile sanctuary today!
